  "api": {
    "url": "POST /api/user-growth/account-performance/platform-performance-placeholder-table",
    "method": "POST",
    "priority": "P1",
    "requestBody": "dateRangeStart, dateRangeEnd, source?, app?, owner?",
    "responseBody": "platformTotal, accountTotal, platforms"
  },
  "apiSuggestion": {
    "notes": [
      "iconBg/iconColor/iconChar 在占位实现中用于前端徽章展示；真实接口可返回枚举后由前端映射颜色。",
      "若前端将底部文案改为由 platforms 求和，请确保 accountTotal 与各平台 accountCount 一致。"
    ]
  }
